00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:33,192
You fix.

266
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:44,070
Not pigs! No!

267
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:05,353
That's enough!

268
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:10,790
Do you want to use him or kill him?
Bring him up.

269
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:27,477
Master, do what Ironbar says.

270
