is a sleaze pit called Bartertown.

407
01:01:14,560 --> 01:01:17,677
If the earth doesn't swallow you up,
that place will.

408
01:01:20,400 --> 01:01:23,836
Listen him! There ain't no
Tomorrow-morrow Land!

409
01:01:24,120 --> 01:01:25,712
We done that!

410
01:01:25,960 --> 01:01:28,076
He's got wordstuff out his ass!

411
01:01:28,440 --> 01:01:31,557
Whoever's got the juice,
track with us.

412
01:02:11,680 --> 01:02:13,113
MAX:
Now listen good!

413
01:02:14,560 --> 01:02:19,076
I'm not Captain Walker. I'm the guy
who keeps Mr. Dead in his pocket.

414
01:02:20,480 --> 01:02:22,869
And I say we're gonna stay here.

415
01:02:23,200 --> 01:02:27,034
And we'll live a long time
and we'll be thankful.

416
01:02:28,080 --> 01:02:28,956
Right?

417
01:02:30,880 --> 01:02:32,472
Keep tracking.

418
01:03:25,200 --> 01:03:26,679
MAX:
Slake!

419
01:03:27,520 --> 01:03:28,953
