Is it Tomorrow-morrow Land?

441
01:10:30,680 --> 01:10:32,910
MAX:
No. Bartertown.

442
01:10:34,040 --> 01:10:35,439
It's our only chance.

443
01:10:36,760 --> 01:10:38,716
Get in, we're right behind you.

444
01:10:39,000 --> 01:10:41,070
ANNA:
Wait! Stick together!

445
01:10:41,400 --> 01:10:42,674
ANNA:
Where are we?

446
01:10:43,840 --> 01:10:44,909
MR. SKYFISH:
It's Bartertown.

447
01:10:45,280 --> 01:10:47,157
EDDIE:
It stinks!

448
01:10:47,680 --> 01:10:49,955
MR. SKYFISH:
Tubba, Cusha, wait up!

449
01:10:51,880 --> 01:10:53,154
ANNA:
Which way?

450
01:10:53,720 --> 01:10:55,358
